    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies procedures for EVPN PEs connected to a common
   multihomed site to generate proxy EVPN type 2 IP-&gt;MAC advertisements
   on behalf of other PEs to facilitate preservation of ARP/ND state
   across link or node failures.</t>
